title: Grannys Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Take-out, Asian, Catering, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small place within Rijswijk train station. Has various vegan and vegetarian dishes, all prepared separately from the non-veg ones. Vegan options are labeled in the menu. "Heaven of Delight," once the first vegetarian shop in The Hague, has now a section within Granny's Food. Take away only after 7:30pm.
